<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(من كنيته أَبُو الصَّهْبَاء)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٩٧٧ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّهْبَاء:</span> صلَة بن أَشْيَم الْعَدوي<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>الْبَصْرِيّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> الْحسن، وثابت بن حميد بن هِلَال<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>كناه يُونُس بن عبيد، عَن الْحسن.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٣٩٧٨ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّهْبَاء:</span> صُهَيْب الْبكْرِيّ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عَليّ بن أبي طَالب رَضِي الله عَنهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> الْأَعْمَش.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>قَالَه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٣٩٧٩ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّهْبَاء:</span> الْبَصْرِيّ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> سعيد بن جُبَير.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> الْحسن بن أبي جَعْفَر.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٣٩٨٠ - أَبُو الصَّهْبَاء.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> الضَّحَّاك.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> سُفْيَان بن عُيَيْنَة.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٣٩٨١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّهْبَاء:</span> الْبَصْرِيّ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عبد الله رفاعي، وَالِد عقبَة<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(ق ١٦٧ / ب)</span> .<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> ابْنه عقبَة.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>قَالَه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>٣٩٨٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّهْبَاء:</span> مُضرس بن عبد الله<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>ابْن وهب الوابشي، كُوفِي.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> وَكِيع.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>سَمِعت مُحَمَّد بن يَعْقُوب،<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span> سَمِعت<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>عباسا،<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span> سَمِعت يحيى،<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span><a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>أَبُو الصَّهْبَاء مُضرس بن عبد الله بن وهب.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>٣٩٨٣ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو صَخْرَة:</span> جَامع بن شَدَّاد<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>الْكُوفِي الْمحَاربي.<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span><span class="c5">سمع:</span> طَارق بن عبد الله، وَالْأسود بن هِلَال.<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> سُلَيْمَان الْأَعْمَش، والشيباني،<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>وَشعْبَة، وَقيس وكناه.<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span>٣٩٨٤ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو صَخْرَة:</span> سَلمَة بن دِينَار<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>الْبَصْرِيّ، وَالِد حَمَّاد بن سَلمَة.<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> ابْنه حَمَّاد،<span class="c5"> وَقيل:</span> أَبُو صَخْر.<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>أخبرنَا عَليّ بن مُحَمَّد بن نصر، ثَنَا الْحُسَيْن،<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> سَمِعت عَمْرو بن عَليّ،<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span> حَمَّاد<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span>ابْن سَلمَة بن دِينَار أَبوهُ يكنى أَبَا صَخْر.<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span>٣٩٨٥ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّباح:</span> سُلَيْمَان بن يسير<a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p39"></span>الْكُوفِي.<a href="#p39" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p40"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> إِبْرَاهِيم النَّخعِيّ.<a href="#p40" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p41"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> الثَّوْريّ، وَجَرِير.<a href="#p41" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span>قَالَ عَليّ بن الْمَدِينِيّ، سَمِعت يحيى بن سعيد،<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span><span class="c5">يَقُول:</span> سَأَلت سُفْيَان الثَّوْريّ، عَن قَول<a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p44"></span><span class="c5">إِبْرَاهِيم:</span> <span class="c1">" يُصَلِّي ويداه فِي ثِيَابه "</span> فمطلني أَيَّامًا<a href="#p44" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p45"></span><span class="c5">ثمَّ قَالَ:</span> حَدثنِي بِهِ أَبُو الصَّباح،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> قلت من<a href="#p45" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p46"></span>أَبُو الصَّباح؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سُلَيْمَان بن قَاسم.<a href="#p46" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p47"></span>قَالَ يحيى، وَإِنَّمَا هُوَ سُلَيْمَان بن يسير.<a href="#p47" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>